### ========================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ========================================

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "John Doe"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Current User (Protected - need token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "YOUR_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ========================================
### TEST WITH SAMPLE DATA
### ========================================

### Login as default admin (if exists in schema)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@syncline.local",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### ========================================
### TASKS (Need valid token from login)
### ========================================

### Get all tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get task statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get my tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/my
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get overdue tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create a new task
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Build authentication system",
  "description": "Implement JWT-based authentication with login and register",
  "status": "in_progress",
  "priority": "high",
  "deadline": "2026-02-15T23:59:59"
}

### Get specific task (replace 1 with actual task ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update task status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

### Flag a task as delayed
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1/flag
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Waiting for design approval"
}

### Unflag a task
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/tasks/1/unflag
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}